abstract: "This repository supports a Computers & Chemical Engineering manuscript on PEERFIX2 no-leakage validation of tabular synthetic-data expansion for a small bench-scale biosurfactant DOE dataset. It includes code, data descriptors, validation outputs, figures, and supplementary material for utility, proximity-risk, and domain-grounded concordance analyses."
keywords:
  - biosurfactant
  - synthetic data
  - tabular generative models
  - PEERFIX2
  - domain-grounded concordance
  - design of experiments
  - small data
